Stapled securities

stapled securities are classified as equity and entitle the holder to participate in distributions and on winding up of the Group in proportion to the number of securities held. Every holder of a stapled security present at a meeting, in person or by proxy, is entitled to one vote. The issued units of the Group are made up of a parcel of stapled securities, each parcel comprising one share in THL, one unit in THT and one share in TlL. The individual securities comprising a parcel of stapled securities cannot be traded separately.
